channel.title: [659]Uncalled Attack - I tried and got fucked over yet again
channel.description:
Some sort of divine power doesn't want me to have a development team, I got screwed again. Thank you whichever developer deleted all the files [I assume pk2play]. Pk2play, why do I assume you? You're the only one that constantly flamed in my forums, raged at my players, just constant disrespect. I do hope none of you think down towards him just because he ruined my project, I'll make another one in time.
Thank all of you members out there for your support; honestly, thank you. It just seems that I try to do my best to help the community, I try to speed up the process with a team and always get fucked over in the end. I won't be near as gullible as this anymore, I'm never going to work with a team. Please don't take this personally, I just can't seem to make a project without getting fucked over in the long-run.
Sorry this all happened, I wish it hadn't.
